==English==

===Pronunciation===
*bro͞oz, /bruːz/, /<tt>bru:z</tt>/
*:'''Homophones''': [[brew]]s
*:[[Rhymes:English:-uːz|Rhymes: -uːz]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# (''medical'') A [[purplish]] [[mark]] on the [[skin]] due to [[leakage]] of [[blood]] from [[capillary|capillaries]] under the surface that have been damaged by a [[blow]].
# A dark mark on [[fruit]] caused by a blow to its surface.

====Synonyms====
*(''medical''): [[contusion]] (''technical term'')

